data.description: GORGEOUS 5 Bedrooms, 3.5 Baths Home! Located in a WORLD CLASS GOLF CLUB OF HOUSTON COMMUNITY! Country Club Style Living w/ Luxury, Healthy, Quiet Life ENJOYING STAY-CATIONS EVERY DAY! This Amazing Home has a Stunning GOURMET KITCHEN w/Custom Cabinetry, LARGE WALK-IN PANTRY, Granite Countertops, GE Profile SS Appliances. REFRIGERATOR STAYS! 3 HVAC UNITS! SPACIOUS PRIMARY SUITE w/Designer Custom Ceiling & ITS OWN A/C UNIT! Primary Bath has GARDEN JACUZZI TUB, Double Vanities, 2 Walk-In Closets & Built-Ins. 2 FIREPLACES, In Living Rm & a DOUBLE-SIDED FIREPLACE In Dining Rm/Exec Study Room. Cozy MEDIA ROOM! Enormous GAME ROOM! Lovely ART NITCHES! 3-CAR GARAGE w/ SINK & CUSTOM BUILT-IN CABINETS and a REFRIGERATOR! 2 ATTICS! ALARM SYSTEM! POOL-SIZE BACKYARD, Gorgeous EXTENDED COVERED PATIO w/Water/Gas Connections & Outdoor Speakers. NEW A/C UNIT, 2 WATER HEATERS & FENCE Replaced in 2022! 15 Min f/Downtown, 10 Min f/IAH!
